Package civitas.celestis.math.vector

Interface IntVector<V extends IntVector<V,F>,F extends FloatVector<F>>

Type Parameters:
V - Itself (the parameter and result of various operations)
F - The float vector corresponding to the size of this vector
All Superinterfaces:
Collectable<Integer>, Group<Integer>, Listable<Integer>, Serializable, Vector<Integer,V>
All Known Implementing Classes:
Int2, Int3, Int4
public interface IntVector<V extends IntVector<V,F>,F extends FloatVector<F>> extends Vector<Integer,V>
A vector which uses the type int.
